projects.name: WEATHER API
projects.description: My weather API project provides real-time weather data for any location in the world. Users can input a city and receive up-to-date information on temperature, precipitation, and more. Designed and developed a web application that provides real-time weather updates based on user's location. Implemented APIs from various weather sources to ensure accuracy and reliability of weather information.

projects.name: FOOD RECIPE
projects.description: A food recipe web application for creating and getting recipes. Users can create, edit, delete recipes, including instructions, ingredients, and images. Features: Searching and filtering, recipe management, favorite and ratings, user authentication and authorization, database management.

projects.name: CHAT APP
projects.description: User can register and their credentials and chat remains private. A full stack web chatApp made using Mern stack, User can also view the online status of other users in their chat list. Hi-Five is a Full Stack Chatting App. Uses Socket.io for real time communication and stores user details in encrypted format in Mongo DB Database.
